snippet.title: Game Boy Advance - Konjiki no Gash Bell!! Yuujou no Dengeki Dream Tag Tournament © 2005 Banpresto
snippet.description:
DESCRIPTION
Konjiki no Gash Bell!! Yuujou no Dengeki Dream Tag Tournament is an Action game, developed and published by Banpresto, which was released in Japan in 2005.
